  "2026-05-23T08:30:09.880Z",codex-audit-2026-05-23,"Evidence: Manual isolated temp-project smoke passed in /tmp/pm-cli-manual-final-pass-a7p1FN. create --test cmd=node --version stored command=node --version; update --test cmd=... stored the normalized command; update --test cmd=node --version,name=bad failed with '--test does not recognize key \"name\"'."
  "2026-05-23T08:46:19.116Z",codex-review-subagent-2026-05-23,"Review evidence 2026-05-23 code/contracts subagent: inspected src/cli/commands/create.ts, src/cli/commands/update.ts, src/cli/commands/test.ts, tests/unit/create-command.spec.ts, tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts, tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts. parseTests/create and update now share normalizeStructuredTestEntry: structured --test recognizes command/cmd/path/scope/timeout/timeout_seconds/runtime/assertion/note keys, rejects unknown keys, folds cmd into command, rejects command/cmd conflicts, and preserves bare commands containing equals. pm test --add has matching structured parser semantics and tests for cmd alias, unknown keys, conflicts, and bare equals commands. Focused verification: npm install -g . ok; pm --version 2026.5.18; node -v v25.9.0; pnpm -v 10.33.0; pnpm build ok; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/plan-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts -> 4 files passed, 170 tests passed. No parser correctness findings; no files changed by reviewer."
  "2026-05-23T08:50:07.790Z",codex-dogfood-subagent-2026-05-23,"Focused --test dogfood evidence 2026-05-23 (codex-dogfood-subagent-2026-05-23): PASS in isolated temp root /tmp/pm-cli-manual-dogfood.tCuYuD using node dist/cli.js. create --test cmd= normalized to command=\"node --version\"; update --test cmd= appended commands=[\"node --version\",\"pnpm --version\"]. Unknown --test key rejection covered both create and update: create exit=2, code=command_failed; update exit=2, code=command_failed. Dedicated pm test link also passed; projected item links show tests=2. No blocker found for cmd alias or unknown-key rejection behavior in this build."
  "2026-05-23T09:17:07.049Z",codex-linked-test-verifier,"Linked-test UX verifier evidence 2026-05-23: inspected src/cli/commands/create.ts, src/cli/commands/test.ts, tests/unit/create-command.spec.ts, tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts, tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts. Verdict: behavior passes for pm-swie. create/update --test now use the same structured linked-test keys as pm test --add via linked-test-entry helper semantics: cmd normalizes to command, unknown keys in structured entries are rejected, command/cmd conflicts are rejected, and bare commands containing = remain bare commands. Commands run: npm install -g .; pm --version => 2026.5.18; node -v => v25.9.0; pnpm -v => 10.33.0; pnpm build => pass; PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts --reporter=dot => 3 files passed, 144 tests passed. Suggested fix before commit: ensure new src/cli/commands/linked-test-entry.ts is tracked, because create.ts imports it and git status currently shows it untracked. No files edited by verifier."
