  "2026-05-23T09:37:04.953Z",codex-linked-test-specialist,"Specialist review 2026-05-23: reused closed child pm-swie under active parent pm-rnpb; did not create a duplicate item. Reviewed current linked-test parsing changes around src/cli/commands/linked-test-entry.ts, create/test parser reuse, create/update/test parser tests, and contracts spec changes. Decision: no further code change from this specialist; current parser behavior covers --add/--test cmd alias, unknown structured-key rejection, command/cmd conflict rejection, and bare commands containing equals, including uppercase structured keys in the current tests/helper. Verification passed: PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts --reporter=dot => 3 files passed, 144 tests passed; PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts --reporter=dot => 1 file passed, 17 tests passed. Remaining risk: src/cli/commands/linked-test-entry.ts is still untracked in git status, so commit prep must include it with the imports."
